| `service_credentials_file` | The path to your Google service account json file. See earlier documentation for how<br>to [authenticate using service account credentials](https://firebase.google.com/docs/app-distribution/ios/distribute-fastlane#service-acc-fastlane). |
| `service_credentials_json_data` | Google service account json file content. See earlier documentation for how<br>to [authenticate using service account credentials](https://firebase.google.com/docs/app-distribution/ios/distribute-fastlane#service-acc-fastlane). |
| `debug` | A boolean flag. You can set this to `true`<br>to print verbose debug output. |

